Package: xubuntu-artwork
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, murrine-themes
Recommends: xubuntu-plymouth-theme, xubuntu-gdm-theme, xubuntu-wallpapers,
 xubuntu-icon-theme
Description: Xubuntu themes and artwork
 This package contains Xubuntu themes and artwork.

Package: xubuntu-wallpapers
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Xubuntu Wallpapers
 The default Wallpapers for Xubuntu.

Package: xubuntu-gdm-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, gdm
Recommends: gnome-settings-daemon, xfwm4
Suggests: xfce4-power-manager
Provides: gdm-theme
Description: Xubuntu GDM greeter theme
 The GDM greeter theme used for a standalone Xubuntu installation.
 .
 This package can also be safely installed on other Ubuntu desktops desiring to
 use this theme.

Package: xubuntu-plymouth-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-label
Description: Plymouth theme for Xubuntu
 The Plymouth theme for Xubuntu

Package: xubuntu-icon-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, elementary-icon-theme
Description: Xubuntu icon theme
 The default icon theme for Xubuntu.
